{"tid":1124411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府部門都玩復仇者？","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T05:47:02.000Z","uid":104849,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52c94483beffa953270b5fcf442ce8fa1edc4b00","tid":1124411,"uid":104849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"政府部門都玩復仇者？香港吉祥物任何仁、大嘥鬼組成 Assemble For Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n近年政府不同部門都用到吉祥物宣傳訊息，適逢 Avengers 4《復仇者聯盟 4：終局之戰》上映，各部門的社交媒體均向電影「致敬」，將七個吉祥物合組成「Assemble for Hong Kong」，實現最新的「跨部門合作」。<br />\n<br />\n參與的專頁有七個，香港消防處、香港天文台、清潔龍阿德、B仔自然教室、匿獅 Lion、大嘥鬼和滴惜仔，每個專頁均上載七個吉詳物的合照，而專頁的主角就會放在中間。此外，每個專頁亦上載了吉祥品的單人相片，下方就有字句介紹角色，而紅底白字的角色名字亦甚具 Marvel 標誌的特色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3axfLr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3axfLr.png&h=9a90ad39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2Drkb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2Drkb7.png&h=cd523b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GezuhYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGezuhYO.png&h=b2ff7c76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFsfXYP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFsfXYP.png&h=0f56956a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NHLALv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NHLALv.png&h=71230e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zazFpDR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzazFpDR.png&h=51aa4fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Y3iVLx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Y3iVLx.png&h=85841bad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/say3nqy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsay3nqy.png&h=fecad615&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"256a3f930ee6e7bfb971b78922dbdbf6583963a5","tid":1124411,"